**TDS (Tax Deducted at Source)** is tax collected at the point of payment. Employers deduct TDS on salary, banks deduct TDS on FD interest above ₹40,000 (₹50,000 for seniors), and deductors deduct TDS on rent, professional fees, and commissions at applicable rates. This calculator covers all major TDS categories.
